<B>__{gabe}
<A>__{just runs straight ahead to ryan, getting to him before the machine gun field of fire can intersect his path gabe tackles ryan as he manages to get the goggles off both men fall to the ground, and the machine gun clatters away, landing on the edge of the ice, just out of reach ryan, now recovered from the blinding flash, pulls an ice axe out of a pack sheath and swings it at gabe gabe rolls away in time, and gets to the machine gun, grabbing it but ryan dives for gabe, slamming into him the force of it knocks the machine gun loose it skips down the ice slope but the momentum of ryan's hit also carries both gabe and ryan over the edge, onto }
