<A>__{finally grabs the ice axe, pulling it off ryan's wrist just as they reach the precipice edge, gabe loops the axe to his wrist and swings toward the ice with everything he's got the axe's scythe like blade catches on the ice, right at the lip of the precipice gabe is wrenched to a painful halt, suspended over the drop, as what's left of ryan, still screaming, shoots over the edge gabe unhooks the axe, and gets another handhold. gabe uses the axe to climb further down the ice to some rock finding easier hand holds, he quickly disappears into the darkness. qualen, kristel and kynette look down ryan's death scream is still echoing. qualen is furious gabe has escaped with the second case.}
